These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Cigar: fonseca, siglo, ritmeester, baccarat
House: palace, craftsman, townhouse, wooden
1. Cigar:ritmeester is between House:townhouse and House:craftsman##2
2. Cigar:baccarat is on the left or right of House:townhouse##3
3. House:townhouse is not to the left of House:townhouse##8
4. House:craftsman != Cigar:ritmeester##6
5. Cigar:ritmeester is somewhere to the right of Cigar:fonseca##5
6. Cigar:fonseca is on the right of House:palace##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | fonseca | ritmeester | siglo  |
| House   | palace | townhouse   | wooden  | craftsman |

