.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Flower: dahlia, aconite, amaryllis, tulip
Music-Genre: trance, folk, punk, pop
1. Music-Genre:pop is not to the left of Music-Genre:pop##8
2. Flower:dahlia is somewhere to the right of Flower:tulip##5
3. Flower:dahlia == Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Flower:tulip is between Flower:dahlia and Flower:aconite##2
5. Flower:aconite is somewhere between Flower:amaryllis and Music-Genre:trance##7
6. Music-Genre:punk is somewhere to the left of Flower:aconite##5
7. Music-Genre:trance is not to the left of Music-Genre:trance##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | amaryllis | aconite          | tulip | dahlia     |
| Music-Genre    | punk      | pop | trance | folk |

