2. Sport:soccer is on the far left##1
3. Hobby:photography is on the right of Hobby:dancing##1
4. Hobby:photography is in an even position##4
5. Hobby:singing is on the far left or far right##3
6. Hobby:dancing is somewhere to the left of Sport:badminton##5
7. Hobby:singing == Sport:handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | dancing | photography | hiking     | singing |
| Sport   | soccer    | badminton   | basketball | handball    |

